node.text:
ASMR Pokémon Unboxing is back 👀🍃👏🏻

This is a post featured with @cardgameclubit which is one of the best Pokémon online store that I’ve ever seen!🤩👏🏻 I received a full box as you can see of the serie ‘Battle Styles’ and look what I pulled!😭 One of the best card (in my opinion) of this set and I’m very happy that I found it!
Watch the entire video to check out all the cards that I found and be sure to check the page of Card Game Club!💕⠀

node.text:
ASMR Pokémon Unboxing!👀Guys this is the video unboxing in partnership with @fantasiastore.it that sent me these awesome Pokémon’s products that you can see here!!🤧 This is also one of the best Online Shop I ever seen about Pokémon cards and be sure to check it out please!!👀💞 Obviously is not only about Pokémon but you can find also some manga/anime stuff like action figures and funkos!🤩

I wasn’t that lucky like you could see but still had a lot of fun while doing this video!🤣
I hope you enjoyed the video!💕

node.text:
ASMR Pokémon Unboxing 👀🔥
⠀
This is to celebrate the partnership with @pokemonstore24 which Pokèmon’s online Shop is amongst the best I ever visited! Is not just affidabile and safe, but their shipping is really quick and, if you spend more than 89€, free! 😱
⠀
I received a Lapis Graad 10 card which is absolutely stunning! I completely fell in love with it! Also, they gave me a lucky “booster box Shiny V star” (JAP)! I found a wonderful Charizard Vmax Shiny😍🔥
⠀
The shop’s link is “ www.pokemonstore.it “, for any possibile question, you can also contact them on their IG page @pokemonstore24 👍🏻
⠀
I hope you like this video and be sure to check their website!🥰

node.text:
My Anemo’s squad is finally finished! Which one is your favorite?👀🍃🤔
⠀
In the last period I had a lot of busy days mostly because of the shop, but finally I had time to finish this piece and I felt in love with it!!😭😍
Seeing all of them together makes me so happy and aaaa I wanna draw the other characters as well now!🥺 I’m planning to draw Ayaka next because she’s one of my favorite after Hu Tao but I still didn’t decided yet so if you have any request just ask me under this post!☺️ I really loved the combination of these colors, I guess I’m improving on it so I’m glad!😁 I really hope that you liked this drawing and all the serie as well! Cya!💕

node.text:
Does my art looks like me?🙈👀🤔
⠀
Ahhhh okay now I’m definitely SHY but I decided to post because why not? 😆👏🏻 Basically I read everyday comments like “omg you really looks like you art!” “This drawing definitely seems you!”😲
I’m always like “no-“ because I can’t actually notice it but does it really like this?🤣👌🏻 My pic with my little cat Danny is my fave between all btw uwu 💕
ANYWAY- I hope you appreciate as the little chibi ver. of me!😆 see ya!💖
.
.
.
#artvsartist oh btw I took inspiration from @/minawa_nanami uwu #artistchallenge #artchallenge #artwork #animeboy #mangaboy #manga #anime #animefanart #fanarts #animearts #digitalarts #otakuboy

⠀
I decided to make this drawing of Ash Lynx from #bananafish because I didn’t know who I could draw so when I thought about him sounded perfect to me!🤣👌🏻 I also made some cute pins of a few starters and I really enjoyed doing them!😼
⠀
The shop’s link is “fantasiastore. it” and for any questions you can contact them on their IG page @fantasiastore.it , very quickly reply guaranteed!🤩 
I hope you like the drawing and see you with a new one!😉💕
